    </header>

    <main style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; flex-direction: column;">
        <h1 class="page-title" style="color: #fff;">Available Subjects</h1>
        <div class="subjects-grid">
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>JAVA</h3>
                <p>Test your JAVA skills with our comprehensive exam.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('java')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>Physics</h3>
                <p>Challenge yourself with physics problems and concepts.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('physics')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>Chemistry</h3>
                <p>Explore chemical reactions and molecular structures.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('chemistry')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>Biology</h3>
                <p>Dive into the world of life sciences and organisms.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('biology')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>Computer Science</h3>
                <p>Test your programming and computer fundamentals.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('computer-science')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
            <div class="subject-card">
                <h3>English</h3>
                <p>Assess your language and comprehension skills.</p>
                <button class="take-test-btn" onclick="startExam('english')">Take Test</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>

